      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">3</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 26.3 - 老子 26.5</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 26.3 - 老子 26.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>是以聖人終日行不離輜重。雖有榮觀，燕處超然。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Therefore a wise prince, marching the whole day, does not go far from his baggage waggons. Although he may have brilliant prospects to look at, he quietly remains (in his proper place), indifferent to them.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-026__align-004">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
